body:
Okay, may be the best app of 2k16/17 in my opinion. It pushes people who love the game and are intreiged by it to go out and catch some pokemon while excerising. As a child when I played pokemon, I dreamed of having it come to life and this is almost as close as it gets! It does drain your battery though...Please keep your hatred if you have some to yourself. I think the game is AMAZING and its bringing people together in these rough times. It's just what we needed.
Answer these questions!

4. What is your player name?
5. Who was your starter?
